.TH STRATUS-AI 1 "June 2026" "stratus-ai 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
stratus-ai \- assess cloud and external security exposure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stratus-ai
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
StratusAI performs cloud and external security assessments with optional AI
synthesis. External scans and raw JSON output work without an AI API key.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-mode " " MODE
Select internal, external, or both.
.TP
.BR \-\-target " " HOST
Set the hostname or IP for external assessment.
.TP
.B \-\-no-ai
Skip AI analysis and write raw scanner output.
.TP
.BR \-\-provider " " PROVIDER
Select aws or gcp for cloud assessment.
.SH EXAMPLE
.B stratus-ai --mode external --target example.org --no-ai
